				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ Enrichmentscore=\raisebox{1ex}{$\frac{m}{n}$}\!\left/ \!\raisebox{-1ex}{$\frac{M}{N}$}\right. $$\end{document}Enrichmentscore=mnMN.
